					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I see you use a CLI to enable vblank NMI? SEI and CLI only affect IRQ, not NMI. If you're never going to use IRQs, the simplest solution would be a SEI at the start of your program (like you have right now), and never ever use CLI.
<br />
<br />The cleaner solution would be to use SEI like above, and disable every IRQ 'generator', like the APU frame sequencer IRQ.</div>

